notesStmt.note: Much damaged. All folios restored, stuck on paper.
All the leaves are slightly worm-eaten and/or stained.
One leaf missing after folio 43 and 45 respectively.
Manuscript description based on Margoliouth, G.: Catalogue of the Hebrew and Samaritan Manuscripts in the British Museum, London 1965.

msContents.summary: Several fragments of Judeo-Arabic commentaries on the Hagiographa.

msItem.title: Commentary on the Song of Songs
